WEBVTT

00:01.236 --> 00:03.742
<i>PREVIOUSLY</i>
<i>ON "WAYWARD PINES"...</i>

00:03.742 --> 00:06.347
THIS FAKE LITTLE TOWN
IS ALL THAT'S LEFT.

00:07.216 --> 00:08.385
THERE'S A FACTION.

00:08.385 --> 00:10.457
THEY'RE GONNA TAKE DOWN
THE FENCE.

00:10.457 --> 00:12.594
SURRENDER YOUR ARMS AND
EXPLOSIVES BY TOMORROW MORNING

00:12.594 --> 00:15.267
AND EVERYTHING
STAYS BETWEEN US.

00:15.267 --> 00:18.474
WAYWARD PINES
NEEDS A NEW GENERATION.

00:18.474 --> 00:20.479
YOU AND BEN
LOOK SO NICE TOGETHER.

00:20.479 --> 00:21.748
HOW IS
THAT WORKING OUT?

00:21.748 --> 00:23.518
IT'S GREAT, ACTUALLY.

00:23.518 --> 00:26.125
YOU WERE RIGHT.
THEY GOT TO ETHAN.

00:26.125 --> 00:27.728
WE EXECUTE TONIGHT.

00:27.728 --> 00:30.367
Ethan: ALL RIGHT. WHO'S THAT?
Nurse Pam: TED LAUFER.

00:30.367 --> 00:32.138
HE DRIVES
THE DELIVERY TRUCK.

00:32.138 --> 00:34.108
HE'S ALWAYS RIGHT ON TIME,
RIGHT AT 8:00.

00:34.108 --> 00:35.612
Okay, let's go.

00:41.658 --> 00:43.797
HELP!

00:43.797 --> 00:46.135
I NEED A DOCTOR!

00:46.135 --> 00:47.539
HELP!

00:47.539 --> 00:50.144
COME HERE.
COME HERE.

00:50.144 --> 00:51.681
I NEED A DOCTOR.
SIR, WE CAN HELP.

00:51.681 --> 00:53.084
Woman: YOU'RE OKAY.

00:53.084 --> 00:55.155
COME WITH US, PLEASE.

00:56.692 --> 00:57.794
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATION ]

00:57.794 --> 01:00.233
WHAT HAPPENED?
TRUCK EXPLODED.

01:00.233 --> 01:01.703
PREP RADIOLOGY, NOW!

01:02.538 --> 01:04.075
OH, MY GOD!

01:04.075 --> 01:05.645
WAIT A MINUTE.
IS THIS GUY A REAL DOCTOR?

01:05.645 --> 01:08.251
OF COURSE HE IS.
WE NEED TO MOVE!

01:08.251 --> 01:10.188
BEN WILL RECEIVE
THE BEST POSSIBLE CARE.

01:10.188 --> 01:12.527
YOU KNOW THE CHILDREN
ARE OUR MOST PRECIOUS RESOURCE.

01:13.796 --> 01:15.400
Man:
<i>PAM TO ICU, PLEASE.</i>

01:15.400 --> 01:16.603
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATION ]

02:01.702 --> 02:03.840
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

02:03.840 --> 02:05.644
Nurse Pam:
TRY TO REMAIN CALM.

02:05.644 --> 02:08.584
GO AHEAD AND LOOK.
THERE YOU GO.

02:08.584 --> 02:09.887
HEY.
OH, MY GOD.

02:11.390 --> 02:12.794
[ GASPS ]

02:12.794 --> 02:15.499
[ SNIFFLES ]
AH, HERE'S DR. CAROL.

02:15.499 --> 02:18.706
SO FAR, I SEE NO
SIGNIFICANT INJURY TO HIS BRAIN,

02:18.706 --> 02:20.177
BUT WE WON'T KNOW
EXACTLY WHERE WE STAND

02:20.177 --> 02:21.279
UNTIL HE REGAINS
CONSCIOUSNESS.

02:21.279 --> 02:22.849
BUT HE'S GONNA BE OKAY.

02:22.849 --> 02:24.452
IF HE COMES TO
IN THE NEXT 24 HOURS,

02:24.452 --> 02:27.192
THE ODDS OF A FULL RECOVERY
ARE VERY GOOD.

02:27.192 --> 02:29.864
IT COULD BE A LONG NIGHT.
TRY TO GET SOME REST.

02:34.575 --> 02:37.247
WHAT KIND OF PERSON SETS OFF
A BOMB IN THE MIDDLE OF TOWN?

02:37.247 --> 02:39.185
I TOLD HIM TO STAY HOME.
Ethan: HEY.

02:39.185 --> 02:41.591
I DID.
IT'S NOT YOUR FAULT.

02:41.591 --> 02:43.561
HE'S JUST A KID.

02:43.561 --> 02:45.867
HE'S 14.
REMEMBER WHAT YOU WERE LIKE?

02:45.867 --> 02:47.837
DO YOU THINK HE'S INVOLVED
WITH ANY OF THIS?

02:47.837 --> 02:50.176
NO.

02:50.176 --> 02:52.581
[ SIGHS ]

02:52.581 --> 02:54.318
IF YOU NEED ANYTHING
AT ALL,

02:54.318 --> 02:56.457
YOU JUST PRESS THIS BUZZER,
ALL RIGHT?
THANK YOU.

03:01.868 --> 03:04.407
OH, DR. JENKINS!

03:04.407 --> 03:05.644
HOW ARE THE CHILDREN?

03:05.644 --> 03:06.712
AMY BRESLOW'S
GONNA BE ALL RIGHT,

03:06.712 --> 03:08.316
ALL THINGS CONSIDERED.

03:08.316 --> 03:09.853
BEN BURKE
IS STILL UNCONSCIOUS.

03:09.853 --> 03:12.292
BUT NOT TO WORRY --
DR. CAROL IS WITH HIM.

03:12.292 --> 03:14.697
HE'S ABSOLUTELY GOING
TO PULL THROUGH.

03:14.697 --> 03:16.701
HOW HAVE THEY BEEN
ABLE TO DO THIS?!

03:16.701 --> 03:19.441
SETTLE YOURSELF DOWN,
NOW.

03:19.441 --> 03:23.416
REMEMBER WHERE YOU ARE
FOR GOD'S SAKE, DAVID.

03:23.416 --> 03:26.958
W-WE'LL PUT OUT AN ISSUE
OF THE <i>CHRONICLE.</i>

03:26.958 --> 03:28.962
WE EXPLAIN THIS IS A --

03:28.962 --> 03:30.699
IT'S A -- AN EXPLOSION.
IT'S A GAS LEAK.

03:30.699 --> 03:32.002
YES.

03:32.002 --> 03:35.710
IT'S A FINE IDEA.
I JUST HOPE THEY BUY IT.

03:35.710 --> 03:37.580
I'M WORRIED
ABOUT THE TOWNSFOLK.

03:37.580 --> 03:40.989
AND PEOPLE HAVE
ALREADY STARTED TALKING.

03:40.989 --> 03:43.360
I THINK WE SHOULD
DO SOMETHING FOR THEM,

03:43.360 --> 03:46.033
SOMETHING VERY, VERY SPECIAL,
FOR THE ENTIRE COMMUNITY.

03:46.033 --> 03:47.503
A CELEBRATION?

03:47.503 --> 03:49.374
YES.

03:49.374 --> 03:53.750
YES, A CELEBRATION OF LIFE
IN WAYWARD PINES.

03:53.750 --> 03:58.994
REMIND EVERYBODY EXACTLY HOW
BLESSED WE ACTUALLY ARE.

03:58.994 --> 04:00.732
HMM?

04:04.673 --> 04:06.678
[ SNIFFS ]

04:11.689 --> 04:16.567
THIS IS INTERNAL BLEEDING.
IT'S BAD.

04:16.567 --> 04:18.036
WE SHOULD KEEP MOVING.

04:18.036 --> 04:21.778
NO. NO. NO,
WE HAVE TO STAY HERE

04:21.778 --> 04:23.048
AND WAIT FOR THE OTHERS.

04:23.048 --> 04:25.052
NO ONE'S COMING, HAROLD.
WE DON'T KNOW THAT.

04:25.052 --> 04:27.758
AND HE IS NOT GONNA SURVIVE
ANOTHER MOVE.

04:27.758 --> 04:30.030
[ MAN WHISTLES ]

04:30.030 --> 04:33.604
HERE THEY COME.
THANK GOD.

04:33.604 --> 04:35.609
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

04:44.361 --> 04:47.702
I GOT SOME FOOD, WATER,
AND FIRST AID IN THERE.

04:47.702 --> 04:49.038
WAIT.
WHAT'S RUBY DOING?

04:49.038 --> 04:50.509
SHE HAD TO GO BACK.

04:50.509 --> 04:52.412
SHE CAN'T RISK
SHOWING UP LATE FOR WORK.

04:53.916 --> 04:55.486
WHAT HAPPENED TO ERIC?

04:55.486 --> 04:57.390
HE GOT PINNED BETWEEN
THE TRUCK AND THE DUMPSTER.

04:57.390 --> 04:58.527
WELL, WE SHOULD TAKE HIM
DOWN TO THE HOSPITAL.

04:58.527 --> 05:00.497
SO THEY CAN EXECUTE HIM?

05:00.497 --> 05:01.967
WHAT HAPPENED
AT THE FENCE?

05:01.967 --> 05:05.040
TWO GOT AWAY, FOUR GOT TAKEN,
AND KATE'S IN JAIL.

05:05.040 --> 05:06.912
OH, MY GOD.
LOOK.

05:06.912 --> 05:10.886
I REALLY WANT TO HELP YOU GUYS,
BUT I CAN'T STAY.

05:10.886 --> 05:12.758
SORRY.

05:17.869 --> 05:23.147
Kate: [ Distorted ]
I WANT TO GET OUT OF THIS TOWN!

05:23.147 --> 05:24.717
WHY?

05:24.717 --> 05:27.457
BECAUSE
NONE OF IT'S REAL.

05:27.457 --> 05:30.463
IT'S A --
IT'S A POTEMKIN VILLAGE.

05:30.463 --> 05:32.868
THEY HAVE THEM IN -- IN SYRIA,
NORTH KOREA.

05:32.868 --> 05:35.140
THEY'RE FAKE CITIES
BUILT TO IMPRESS.

05:35.140 --> 05:38.481
[ SOBS, MUMBLES ]

05:38.481 --> 05:41.888
WHO'S BEHIND IT?
CIA?

05:43.659 --> 05:45.931
IS IT SOCIAL OR --
OR MEDICAL?

05:45.931 --> 05:47.668
WHAT?

05:47.668 --> 05:50.908
THIS GOVERNMENT EXPERIMENT.
IS IT SOCIAL OR MEDICAL?

05:50.908 --> 05:52.946
IT'S JUST A TOWN.

05:52.946 --> 05:55.051
[ Crying ] JUST A TOWN.

05:55.051 --> 05:57.657
WITH AN ELECTRIFIED FENCE?

05:57.657 --> 06:01.632
W-W-W-WITH A MICROCHIP
IN MY LEG?!

06:04.639 --> 06:07.913
YOU HAVE TO WRITE
THAT DOWN, HUH?

06:07.913 --> 06:10.051
I'M JUST NOTING
YOUR PROGRESS.

06:10.051 --> 06:13.058
I'M NOT MAKING
ANY PROGRESS.

06:13.058 --> 06:16.632
I DON'T WANT TO MAKE
ANY PROGRESS.

06:16.632 --> 06:21.075
I WANT TO TALK TO SOMEONE
IN CHARGE NOW!

06:21.075 --> 06:24.683
IT'S BEEN TWO MONTHS!

06:26.821 --> 06:29.159
I -- I AM SORRY.

06:29.159 --> 06:31.164
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

06:31.164 --> 06:35.640
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

06:35.640 --> 06:37.812
OH, POOR KATIE.

06:37.812 --> 06:39.950
NOT FEELING SO WELL, EH?

06:39.950 --> 06:44.460
DON'T WORRY.
WE'LL GET YOU ALL FIXED UP.

06:44.460 --> 06:45.997
[ SOBS ]

06:45.997 --> 06:48.469
THAT'S A GOOD GIRL.

06:48.469 --> 06:50.473
[ WHIMPERS ]

06:50.473 --> 06:52.745
OH, SHH, SHH, SHH, SHH,
SHH, SHH, SHH, SHH.

06:52.745 --> 06:54.883
[ GASPS ]

06:56.954 --> 06:59.093
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

07:18.235 --> 07:21.141
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]
Woman: RUBY'S HERE, YOU GUYS.

07:24.816 --> 07:27.555
HEARD THE DRIVER AND TWO KIDS
ARE STILL IN THE HOSPITAL.

07:27.555 --> 07:29.292
Henrietta:
IF THAT WAS THE GAS LINE,

07:29.292 --> 07:31.163
THEN HOW COME
THE ASPHALT WASN'T DAMAGED?

07:31.163 --> 07:33.836
ONLY THING EXPLODED
WAS THE TRUCK.

07:33.836 --> 07:35.105
HAD TO BE A BOMB.

07:35.105 --> 07:37.912
WHAT DO YOU THINK,
DR. JENKINS?

07:37.912 --> 07:40.651
WELL...

07:40.651 --> 07:42.856
WHEN A DISASTER
LIKE THIS OCCURS

07:42.856 --> 07:44.793
IN A TOWN
AS BEAUTIFUL AS OURS,

07:44.793 --> 07:47.332
IT'S NATURAL
FOR FOLKS TO ASK QUESTIONS.

07:47.332 --> 07:51.642
BUT...WE SHOULD BE CAREFUL
NOT TO SPREAD RUMORS.

07:51.642 --> 07:54.247
[ TELEPHONE RINGING ]

08:00.795 --> 08:02.332
HELLO?

08:05.839 --> 08:07.343
WHO IS IT, RUBY?

08:10.952 --> 08:15.261
A FELLOWSHIP GATHERING,
MANDATORY ATTENDANCE.

08:16.330 --> 08:18.668
[ PEOPLE MURMURING ]

08:29.258 --> 08:30.996
GIVE ME A READING
ON RUBY'S CHIP.

08:32.264 --> 08:35.840
SHE WAS LATE TO WORK.

08:35.840 --> 08:38.245
PINE NEEDLES
IN HER HAIR.

08:40.984 --> 08:45.127
SHE'S AT HOME IN BED.

08:45.127 --> 08:46.997
LET ME SEE.

08:51.073 --> 08:53.078
[ SCOFFS ]

08:53.078 --> 08:54.748
SHE MUST HAVE TAKEN
HER CHIP OUT LAST NIGHT

08:54.748 --> 08:56.117
AND LEFT IT IN HER ROOM.

08:56.117 --> 08:58.690
I WONDER HOW MANY MORE PEOPLE
ARE HOME IN BED.

09:01.128 --> 09:03.000
Ethan: ALL RIGHT,
WHERE ARE THEY, KATE?

09:03.000 --> 09:04.870
FIVE OF YOUR PEOPLE ARE

09:04.870 --> 09:07.109
OFF THE GRID RIGHT NOW,
INCLUDING HAROLD.

09:07.109 --> 09:09.313
YOU THINK I WANT TO HELP YOU
FIND MY HUSBAND?

09:09.313 --> 09:12.087
YOUR HUSBAND BLEW UP A TRUCK
LAST NIGHT ON MAIN STREET.

09:12.087 --> 09:13.890
HE NEARLY
KILLED MY SON.

09:13.890 --> 09:15.761
BEN?

09:15.761 --> 09:18.400
W-WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?
I-IS HE GONNA BE OKAY?

09:18.400 --> 09:20.170
DON'T EVEN SAY HIS NAME.

09:20.170 --> 09:22.409
JUST TELL ME WHERE THEY ARE.
I AM SO SORRY, ETHAN.

09:22.409 --> 09:24.714
SOMETHING MUST HAVE GONE WRONG
WITH THE TIMER.

09:24.714 --> 09:27.053
IT WAS -- IT WAS MEANT
TO GO OFF AT -- AT THE FENCE.

09:27.053 --> 09:30.059
WELL, THAT'S THE LAST THING
THAT WE NEED TO HAVE HAPPEN.

09:30.059 --> 09:33.133
YOU KNOW WHAT THE DIFFERENCE IS
BETWEEN YOU AND ME?

09:33.133 --> 09:35.338
I BELIEVE
WHAT I KNOW IN MY HEART.

09:35.338 --> 09:37.208
YOU BELIEVE
WHAT THEY TELL YOU.

09:37.208 --> 09:38.812
LOOK,
I KNOW YOU DON'T GET IT.

09:38.812 --> 09:40.282
I KNOW YOU THINK
THEY GOT TO ME.

09:40.282 --> 09:42.988
BUT I KNOW WHAT'S OUT THERE
AND IT'S NOT BOISE.

09:42.988 --> 09:45.860
YOU EVER THINK ABOUT WHY
THEY PICKED YOU TO BE SHERIFF?

09:45.860 --> 09:47.164
'CAUSE I HAVE.

09:47.164 --> 09:48.467
YOU KNOW,
I'M GONNA TAKE YOU UP THERE

09:48.467 --> 09:49.936
SO YOU CAN SEE IT
WITH YOUR OWN EYES,

09:49.936 --> 09:50.939
BUT WE DON'T HAVE TIME
WITH THAT NOW.

09:50.939 --> 09:52.241
SEE WHAT?
THE MONSTERS?

09:52.241 --> 09:53.978
WHERE ARE THEY?!

09:53.978 --> 09:55.715
YOU KNOW, YOU HAVE
REALLY GOOD INSTINCTS, ETHAN.

09:55.715 --> 09:58.422
BUT WHEN PUSH COMES TO SHOVE,
YOU WILL ALWAYS FOLLOW ORDERS.

09:58.422 --> 10:01.328
YOU HAVE MADE
THE SAME MISTAKE BEFORE.

10:01.328 --> 10:04.435
WELL...

10:04.435 --> 10:06.774
I'M NOT FOLLOWING ORDERS
THIS TIME.

10:06.774 --> 10:10.148
I'M JUST TRYING TO MAKE SURE
THAT NOBODY GETS KILLED.

10:10.148 --> 10:12.085
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU?

10:12.085 --> 10:16.294
WE WERE PARTNERS?
DON'T YOU TRUST ME AT ALL?

10:16.294 --> 10:20.303
THESE PEOPLE
WANT TO BE FREE.

10:20.303 --> 10:22.174
AND I OWE THEM
THAT CHANCE.

10:31.962 --> 10:34.101
AMY IS HOLDING STEADY,

10:34.101 --> 10:36.873
AND BEN BURKE LOOKS LIKE
HE'LL PULL THROUGH.

10:36.873 --> 10:39.412
RUBY'S ONE OF THEM.

10:39.412 --> 10:42.286
RUBY?

10:42.286 --> 10:44.524
HAVE YOU, UH,
NOTIFIED ETHAN BURKE

10:44.524 --> 10:46.060
SHE NEEDS TO BE
LOCKED UP?

10:46.060 --> 10:48.767
WE NEED TO PUT OUR OWN HOUSE
IN ORDER FIRST.

10:48.767 --> 10:51.172
I'M NOT FOLLOWING.

10:51.172 --> 10:55.013
WE HAVE 24 PEOPLE MANNING
SURVEILLANCE AROUND THE CLOCK.

10:55.013 --> 10:56.784
YET, SOMEHOW,
THESE INSURGENTS

10:56.784 --> 10:59.189
ARE MANAGING TO MEET IN SECRET
AND BUILD BOMBS.

10:59.189 --> 11:00.793
SOMEONE
MUST BE HELPING THEM.

11:00.793 --> 11:02.931
[ SIGHS ]

11:02.931 --> 11:07.942
DAVID,
EVERYONE UP HERE IS FAMILY,

11:07.942 --> 11:10.314
LOYAL TO YOU
TO A FAULT.

11:10.314 --> 11:13.187
SOMEONE'S BETRAYING US AND
WE NEED TO FIND OUT WHO IT IS.

11:13.187 --> 11:16.461
IF IT WILL HELP YOU
TO FEEL BETTER,

11:16.461 --> 11:18.466
I'LL CONDUCT
A FULL SECURITY REVIEW.

11:18.466 --> 11:21.572
YES, IT WOULD
HELP ME FEEL BETTER.

11:32.563 --> 11:34.567
MAN: Snipers have checked
the North quadrant.

11:34.567 --> 11:36.171
All clear.

11:39.078 --> 11:43.454
YOU STILL HAPPY WITH
YOUR DECISION TO JOIN US HERE?

11:43.454 --> 11:46.193
IT'S AN ABSOLUTE PRIVILEGE
TO BE HERE.

11:46.193 --> 11:48.064
INDEED. INDEED.

11:48.064 --> 11:50.469
AND WORKING SURVEILLANCE,

11:50.469 --> 11:52.307
IS IT EVER UNCOMFORTABLE
FOR YOU?

11:52.307 --> 11:54.078
DO YOU EVER FEEL
LIKE YOU'RE --

11:54.078 --> 11:56.215
I DON'T KNOW --
INVADING PEOPLE'S PRIVACY?

11:56.215 --> 11:59.089
UH, IT'S THE JOB.

11:59.089 --> 12:00.959
I MEAN, WE DO IT
TO PROTECT THEM, RIGHT?

12:00.959 --> 12:03.531
ABSOLUTELY.
ABSOLUTELY.

12:04.634 --> 12:05.970
HOW'S REGGIE?

12:05.970 --> 12:08.075
VERY GOOD.
AND THE KIDS?

12:08.075 --> 12:10.313
FULL OF ENERGY,
AS ALWAYS.
[ CHUCKLES ]

12:10.313 --> 12:11.583
OH, SUPER GOOD.

12:11.583 --> 12:13.186
HOW ABOUT YOUR POST
AT SURVEILLANCE?

12:13.186 --> 12:14.322
YOU ENJOYING THAT?

12:14.322 --> 12:15.859
I LIKE IT A LOT.

12:15.859 --> 12:18.331
BUT SOMETIMES YOU MIGHT
WANT TO -- I DON'T KNOW --

12:18.331 --> 12:21.938
AVERT YOUR EYES
OR MAYBE EVEN WIPE VIDEO

12:21.938 --> 12:23.877
'CAUSE OF SOMETHING YOU'VE SEEN,
ERASE IT.

12:23.877 --> 12:25.380
ARE YOU KIDDING?

12:25.380 --> 12:28.553
OH, I-I LOVE IT WHEN
THEY LET SOMETHING JUICY SLIP.

12:28.553 --> 12:31.160
[ LAUGHTER ]
VERY GOOD.

12:31.160 --> 12:32.629
SUPER.

12:32.629 --> 12:34.132
THANK YOU SO MUCH,
GINA.

12:34.132 --> 12:35.903
CAN YOU SEND
THE NEXT PERSON IN?

12:35.903 --> 12:38.910
SURE.

12:38.910 --> 12:40.914
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

12:43.119 --> 12:46.660
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]

12:50.168 --> 12:52.574
SWEETIE?
[ GROANS ]

12:52.574 --> 12:55.413
BEN.
SWEETIE. HI.

12:55.413 --> 12:57.484
HOW ARE YOU FEELING?

12:57.484 --> 12:59.488
WATER?

12:59.488 --> 13:02.061
OH, YES. YEAH.

13:02.061 --> 13:04.466
THERE YOU GO, SWEETIE.

13:04.466 --> 13:06.470
DON'T LIFT YOUR HEAD.

13:06.470 --> 13:08.242
YOU HAVE NO IDEA
HOW HAPPY

13:08.242 --> 13:12.116
IT MAKES ME TO SEE YOU
OPEN YOUR EYES.

13:12.116 --> 13:14.255
YOUR DAD AND I
WERE SO SCARED.

13:14.255 --> 13:16.125
WHERE -- WHERE'S AMY?

13:16.125 --> 13:17.662
SHE'S HERE
IN THE HOSPITAL.

13:17.662 --> 13:19.666
IS SHE OKAY?

13:19.666 --> 13:22.473
YEAH, S-SHE'S FINE.

13:22.473 --> 13:24.610
SHE WAS ASKING
ABOUT YOU.

13:24.610 --> 13:26.314
CAN YOU GO CHECK?

13:26.314 --> 13:29.588
YEAH, SURE, I WILL.

13:32.093 --> 13:34.132
I LOVE YOU SO MUCH.

13:42.350 --> 13:44.354
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATION ]

13:55.279 --> 13:57.249
[ GASPS ]

13:57.249 --> 13:58.653
[ SIGHS ]

13:58.653 --> 14:00.122
HOW ARE YOU FEELING?

14:03.096 --> 14:05.234
OH, OKAY, I GUESS.

14:05.234 --> 14:07.238
[ SIGHS ]

14:07.238 --> 14:10.077
OH, BEN.

14:10.077 --> 14:12.082
OH.

14:12.082 --> 14:14.120
EVERYONE IN TOWN
HAS BEEN SO WORRIED ABOUT YOU.

14:14.120 --> 14:16.525
I'M SO RELIEVED
YOU'RE ALL RIGHT.

14:16.525 --> 14:17.762
YEAH, ME TOO.

14:17.762 --> 14:20.734
OH, IT'S JUST TERRIBLE
WHAT'S HAPPENED.

14:20.734 --> 14:23.340
[ SIGHS ] SOMETIMES,
THE CHOICES ONE MAKES

14:23.340 --> 14:25.412
CAN LEAD TO CONSEQUENCES
WE DON'T INTEND.

14:25.412 --> 14:28.084
I NEVER SHOULD HAVE SNUCK OUT
WITH AMY.

14:28.084 --> 14:29.454
OH, NO, NO.

14:29.454 --> 14:31.759
NO, I'M NOT TALKING
ABOUT THAT.

14:31.759 --> 14:35.066
WE WANT YOU TO GROW
YOUR RELATIONSHIPS HERE.

14:35.066 --> 14:37.572
I'M TALKING ABOUT
DECISIONS MADE

14:37.572 --> 14:40.511
BY THE SHERIFF
IN PURSUING THE CASE.

14:42.650 --> 14:46.257
HE'S A GOOD MAN, BEN.
HE'S WELL-INTENTIONED.

14:46.257 --> 14:52.379
AND I'M SURE HE HAD HIS REASONS
FOR LETTING HAROLD BALLINGER GO.

14:52.672 --> 14:55.411
OH, I JUST HOPE
HIS JUDGMENT WASN'T CLOUDED

14:55.411 --> 14:58.418
BY THE FACT THAT HAROLD'S WIFE
IS AN OLD FRIEND OF HIS.

14:58.418 --> 15:02.260
KATE AND YOUR FATHER
ARE FRIENDS, RIGHT?

15:04.364 --> 15:07.103
YEAH, SORT OF.

15:07.103 --> 15:09.375
HE ARRESTED HAROLD
AND THEN HE LET HIM GO.

15:09.375 --> 15:10.812
AND THEN...

15:10.812 --> 15:16.825
I GUESS I JUST DON'T AGREE
WITH THAT KIND OF LENIENCY.

15:16.825 --> 15:20.433
I BELIEVE,
AS DAVID PILCHER BELIEVES,

15:20.433 --> 15:26.179
IN A PHILOSOPHY THAT I LIKE
TO CALL CLEAR AND SEVERE.

15:26.179 --> 15:30.722
CLEAR LAWS
AND SEVERE PUNISHMENTS.

15:30.722 --> 15:34.431
CLEAR AND SEVERE.

15:34.431 --> 15:36.402
TO BE HONEST,

15:36.402 --> 15:39.509
I THINK YOUR FATHER AND I
DISAGREE ON THIS ISSUE.

15:39.509 --> 15:43.250
BUT YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO
GIVE IT SOME THOUGHT.

15:43.250 --> 15:45.121
PEOPLE ARE GONNA
WANT TO HEAR FROM YOU.

15:45.121 --> 15:47.125
WHAT IS
THE PROPER PUNISHMENT

15:47.125 --> 15:51.134
FOR SPEECH OR ACTIONS
THAT HARM WAYWARD PINES?

15:51.134 --> 15:55.143
LENIENCY
OR CLEAR AND SEVERE.

15:55.143 --> 15:56.446
YOU --
YOU SAY THAT PEOPLE

15:56.446 --> 15:58.584
ARE GONNA WANT TO HEAR
WHAT I HAVE TO SAY.

15:58.584 --> 16:00.823
WHAT DOES IT MATTER
WHAT I THINK?

16:00.823 --> 16:05.566
BEN, YOU SURVIVED
A TERRORIST ATTACK.

16:05.566 --> 16:07.203
YOU'RE A HERO NOW.

16:13.384 --> 16:15.722
HOW LONG YOU THINK
WE'RE GONNA SURVIVE OUT HERE?
WE'LL THINK OF SOMETHING.

16:15.722 --> 16:17.726
MM, GOOD.

16:17.726 --> 16:20.165
THAT'S WHAT PEOPLE ALWAYS SAY
WHEN THEY'RE AT THE END.
HEY.

16:20.165 --> 16:23.172
DON'T FALL APART ON ME.

16:23.172 --> 16:25.276
WE'LL THINK
OF SOMETHING.

16:29.853 --> 16:32.192
ERIC.

16:32.192 --> 16:34.430
HEY.

16:44.518 --> 16:46.924
[ GRUNTING ]

16:54.475 --> 16:56.312
I'M NOT DOING THIS
BY MYSELF.

16:56.312 --> 16:57.681
NOT HERE.

16:57.681 --> 17:00.220
WHY DO YOU MEAN?

17:00.220 --> 17:01.723
I'M NOT
GONNA LET HIM ROT

17:01.723 --> 17:03.595
FOR ALL ETERNITY
INSIDE THIS PRISON.

17:03.595 --> 17:05.599
WHAT ARE
YOU TALKING ABOUT?

17:05.599 --> 17:07.336
WE'RE NOT
BURYING HIM HERE.

17:07.336 --> 17:10.476
WE'RE BURYING HIM
IN FREE SOIL

17:10.476 --> 17:12.013
ON THE OTHER SIDE
OF THAT FENCE.

17:12.013 --> 17:14.017
HOW YOU GONNA DO THAT?

17:16.991 --> 17:18.995
Nurse Pam:
YOU EVER FEEL UNCOMFORTABLE

17:18.995 --> 17:20.732
WORKING SURVEILLANCE?

17:20.732 --> 17:25.309
THOUGHTS, FEELINGS, CONCERNS
ABOUT INVASION OF PRIVACY?

17:25.309 --> 17:27.581
OH, NO, NO,
I-I THINK, UM,

17:27.581 --> 17:30.587
OUR METHODS ARE WELL REASONED
AND, UM, NECESSARY

17:30.587 --> 17:33.694
FOR THE CONTINUED...
PRESERVATION OF HUMAN LIFE.

17:33.694 --> 17:35.698
[ Chuckling ] REGGIE,

17:35.698 --> 17:38.003
YOU DON'T HAVE TO QUOTE
THE MANUAL HERE, HMM?

17:38.003 --> 17:43.416
WELL, IN THAT CASE, UM...
SOMETIMES.

17:43.416 --> 17:44.551
UM, A LITTLE BIT.

17:44.551 --> 17:45.955
IT MUST BE STRANGE

17:45.955 --> 17:48.760
PEERING INTO PEOPLE'S LIVES
ALL DAY LONG LIKE THAT.

17:48.760 --> 17:50.030
OH, NO.
I-I-IT'S NOT THAT.

17:50.030 --> 17:52.001
I-I-I KNOW WE'RE HERE
TO PROTECT THEM.

17:52.001 --> 17:53.872
IT'S JUST...

17:53.872 --> 17:56.612
SOMETIMES, PEOPLE SAY,

17:56.612 --> 17:59.484
UH, PERSONAL STUFF.

17:59.484 --> 18:00.888
LIKE WHAT?

18:00.888 --> 18:02.992
MAYBE THEY ASK
CERTAIN QUESTIONS.

18:02.992 --> 18:06.032
LIKE, UH,
"WHAT'S OUTSIDE THE FENCE?"

18:06.032 --> 18:09.506
OR "WHO'S WATCHING
THE CAMERAS?"

18:09.506 --> 18:12.847
AND YOU'RE TELLING ME YOU
DON'T RECORD THOSE INFRACTIONS?

18:12.847 --> 18:15.854
LOOK, I-IF IT'S JUST INNOCENT,
THEN...

18:15.854 --> 18:18.459
THEN SOMETIMES,
I'LL BLUR THE TAPE

18:18.459 --> 18:21.667
OR, I'LL, UH --
I'LL ERASE A SPOT.

18:21.667 --> 18:23.772
BUT I JUST --
I JUST DON'T WANT ANYONE

18:23.772 --> 18:27.881
TO GET IN TROUBLE
FOR JUST ASKING QUESTIONS.

18:27.881 --> 18:30.620
THESE PEOPLE ARE SCARED,
YOU KNOW?

18:30.620 --> 18:32.624
I-I SEE THEM
SOBBING IN THEIR ROOMS,

18:32.624 --> 18:34.395
HOLDING EACH OTHER.

18:34.395 --> 18:38.738
THEY JUST DON'T UNDERSTAND
WHAT BECAME OF THEIR LIVES.

18:40.909 --> 18:44.049
IT'S JUST HUMAN NATURE
TO ASK QUESTIONS.
YEAH.

18:44.049 --> 18:46.789
YEAH, ABSOLUTELY.

18:49.060 --> 18:51.666
HUMAN NATURE.

18:53.738 --> 18:55.608
THANK YOU SO MUCH
FOR COMING IN, REGGIE.

18:55.608 --> 18:56.577
NO PROBLEM.

18:58.047 --> 19:00.052
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

19:16.087 --> 19:18.692
THIS IS A BAD IDEA.

19:18.692 --> 19:21.566
THE CONSTRUCTION CREW
WAS FINISHED FOR THE DAY.

19:21.566 --> 19:22.835
BESIDES, WHO CARES?

19:22.835 --> 19:24.705
IF I'M GONNA DIE,
I'M GONNA DIE TRYING.

19:36.966 --> 19:39.973
[ CARNIVAL MUSIC PLAYING ]

19:43.013 --> 19:45.619
IT'S A WONDERFUL GATHERING,
DON'T YOU THINK?

19:45.619 --> 19:46.955
HMM.

19:46.955 --> 19:50.028
IT'S NICE, BRINGING
EVERYONE TOGETHER LIKE THIS.

19:52.701 --> 19:55.106
THIS WOULD MAKE
A PERFECT TARGET, WOULDN'T IT?

19:55.106 --> 19:57.779
WHOLE TOWN TOGETHER
IN ONE PLACE.

19:57.779 --> 20:00.585
[ COUNTRY MUSIC PLAYING ]

20:00.585 --> 20:01.821
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

20:04.895 --> 20:07.902
I JUST CAME FROM THE HOSPITAL.
TED DIDN'T MAKE IT.

20:07.902 --> 20:09.772
HE'S DEAD?

20:09.772 --> 20:12.511
BURNED OVER 90%
OF HIS BODY.

20:14.516 --> 20:16.988
MAYBE YOU SHOULD
SAY A FEW WORDS, MR. MAYOR.

20:16.988 --> 20:18.124
LIFT THEIR SPIRITS.

20:18.124 --> 20:20.863
THAT'S NOT A BAD IDEA.

20:20.863 --> 20:22.801
[ SNIFFS ]

20:24.238 --> 20:25.707
HEY, FOLKS.

20:25.707 --> 20:27.579
COULD I HAVE
YOUR ATTENTION, PLEASE?

20:27.579 --> 20:29.849
COME ON. MOVE IN HERE,
MOVE IN HERE, MOVE IN HERE.

20:29.849 --> 20:31.821
YEAH, I JUST WANTED
TO WELCOME YOU ALL

20:31.821 --> 20:34.660
TO OUR WONDERFUL
FELLOWSHIP GATHERING.

20:34.660 --> 20:36.699
SO, RELAX, EVERYONE.
HAVE SOME FUN.

20:36.699 --> 20:38.201
HEY,
SAY HELLO TO YOUR NEIGHBOR.

20:38.201 --> 20:40.073
EXCUSE ME.
BECAUSE IT'S JUST
ANOTHER BEAUTIFUL DAY

20:40.073 --> 20:41.943
IN THE FRIENDLIEST PLACE
ON EARTH.

20:41.943 --> 20:43.213
MAYOR,
I'D LIKE TO SAY A WORD.

20:43.213 --> 20:45.217
SHERIFF BURKE,
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN.

20:45.217 --> 20:48.725
[ FEEDBACK ]
LISTEN, FOLKS, THIS REALLY
ISN'T THE BEST TIME FOR THIS.

20:48.725 --> 20:51.063
AS MANY OF YOU MAY HAVE HEARD,
LAST NIGHT,

20:51.063 --> 20:55.239
A BOMB WENT OFF RIGHT HERE
IN THE MIDDLE OF MAIN STREET,

20:55.239 --> 20:56.876
NOT FAR FROM WHERE
YOU PEOPLE ARE STANDING.

20:56.876 --> 20:59.248
AND SEVERAL OF THE PEOPLE
CONNECTED TO THIS CRIME

20:59.248 --> 21:00.685
HAVE GONE MISSING.

21:00.685 --> 21:03.157
SO, UNTIL WE GET
THE SITUATION SORTED OUT,

21:03.157 --> 21:06.130
I THINK IT'S BEST IF EVERYBODY
GOES HOME AND STAYS SAFE.

21:06.130 --> 21:07.867
LET'S WRAP IT UP, PLEASE.

21:07.867 --> 21:09.805
ALL RIGHT, EVERYONE.
YOU HEARD SHERIFF BURKE.

21:09.805 --> 21:11.041
LET'S GO.

21:11.041 --> 21:14.716
WHY DIDN'T YOU
TELL ME ABOUT THIS?

21:14.716 --> 21:17.822
I DIDN'T WANT TO INTERRUPT
YOUR INVESTIGATION.

21:17.822 --> 21:19.225
NOTHING MATTERS MORE

21:19.225 --> 21:23.234
THAN KEEPING THE POPULACE
CALM A-A-AND QUIET.

21:23.234 --> 21:25.105
I'M AFRAID
THE SHIP'S ALREADY SAILED.

21:25.105 --> 21:26.709
[ ARM SCRAPES ]

21:32.154 --> 21:33.891
Hey.

21:33.891 --> 21:34.893
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

21:34.893 --> 21:35.895
HEY.

21:35.895 --> 21:37.632
HOW ARE YOU?

21:39.637 --> 21:41.174
YOU KNOW,
I HAD A CONCUSSION

21:41.174 --> 21:42.878
WHEN I WAS YOUR AGE,
PLAYING FOOTBALL.

21:42.878 --> 21:46.719
I GOT HIT RUNNING A QUICK SLANT
ACROSS THE MIDDLE.

21:46.719 --> 21:49.726
I DON'T REMEMBER TOO MUCH
OF WHAT HAPPENED AFTER THAT.

21:49.726 --> 21:51.865
MY EARS WERE RINGING
FOR A COUPLE OF DAYS.

21:51.865 --> 21:53.869
[ SIGHS ]

21:53.869 --> 21:58.746
SO, GUESS IT HASN'T BEEN
ALL THAT MUCH FUN, HUH?

21:58.746 --> 22:00.150
HEY.

22:00.150 --> 22:01.753
HI.

22:01.753 --> 22:06.029
NO, I GUESS NOT.

22:06.029 --> 22:09.603
ESPECIALLY CONSIDERING THAT
IT ALL COULD HAVE BEEN AVOIDED.

22:09.603 --> 22:12.042
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

22:12.042 --> 22:14.748
YOU HAD THE GUY, DAD.

22:15.918 --> 22:18.256
YOU HAD HIM
AND YOU LET HIM GO.

22:18.256 --> 22:19.893
BEN, WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

22:19.893 --> 22:21.229
YOUR DAD,
HE SAVED YOUR LIFE.

22:21.229 --> 22:22.966
NO, NO, THAT'S OKAY.

22:25.371 --> 22:29.080
I HEARD
THAT YOU ARRESTED THE GUY

22:29.080 --> 22:32.153
WHO MADE THE BOMB
AND THEN YOU LET HIM GO.

22:32.153 --> 22:34.225
WELL, THERE'S A REASON
FOR THAT.

22:34.225 --> 22:37.365
SOMETIMES WE LET A SUSPECT WALK
TO SEE WHERE IT WILL LEAD US.

22:37.365 --> 22:39.837
IT JUST
KIND OF MAKES ME WONDER

22:39.837 --> 22:41.975
IF YOU WOULD HAVE...
I DON'T KNOW.

22:41.975 --> 22:43.712
IF YOU WOULD HAVE
MADE THE SAME DECISION

22:43.712 --> 22:45.148
IF HE WASN'T MARRIED
TO KATE HEWSON.

22:45.148 --> 22:46.886
BEN, THAT'S A TERRIBLE THING
TO SAY.

22:46.886 --> 22:48.022
HE CAN SAY
WHATEVER HE WANTS.

22:49.291 --> 22:52.031
YOU'RE SUPPOSED TO ENFORCE
THE LAWS OF WAYWARD PINES.

22:52.031 --> 22:54.770
YOU'RE NOT SUPPOSED TO BE
LENIENT WITH PEOPLE

22:54.770 --> 22:56.106
BECAUSE YOU KNOW THEM.

22:56.106 --> 22:59.246
[ SIGHS ] HEY.

22:59.246 --> 23:02.253
I WOULD HAVE DONE THE SAME THING
NO MATTER WHO IT WAS.

23:02.253 --> 23:05.994
BEN, IS YOUR TEACHER TELLING YOU
TO SAY ALL OF THIS STUFF?

23:05.994 --> 23:08.768
IS THAT WHAT'S HAPPENING
RIGHT NOW? IS IT THE TEACHER?
NO, HEY.

23:08.768 --> 23:10.070
BEN, IT DOESN'T MATTER.

23:10.070 --> 23:12.275
LOOK.

23:12.275 --> 23:14.747
BEN, WE LOVE YOU.

23:14.747 --> 23:18.288
AND WE'RE JUST -- WE'RE JUST
HAPPY THAT YOU'RE OKAY.

23:18.288 --> 23:20.460
GET --
GET PLENTY OF REST.

23:23.066 --> 23:24.302
HEY.
HEY.

23:24.302 --> 23:25.304
HI, AMY.

23:25.304 --> 23:27.308
LOOK WHO'S HERE.

23:27.308 --> 23:29.447
WE'LL TALK ABOUT THIS
LATER.

23:33.422 --> 23:35.760
HI.

23:44.046 --> 23:46.183
SO,
NO ONE IN SURVEILLANCE

23:46.183 --> 23:49.190
IS BREAKING ANY RULES OR --
OR PROTOCOLS.

23:49.190 --> 23:53.065
WELL, IF THERE'S A PROBLEM,
IT MUST BE A SOFTWARE GLITCH.

23:56.305 --> 23:59.747
NEVER HAD TO PUNISH ANYONE
ON THE INSIDE BEFORE.

23:59.747 --> 24:00.916
NO.

24:00.916 --> 24:03.121
IT'D BE A TERRIBLE LINE
TO CROSS.

24:03.121 --> 24:05.727
AND HAPPILY,
WE DON'T HAVE TO.

24:05.727 --> 24:07.798
NO ONE IS
HELPING THE INSURGENTS.

24:10.036 --> 24:13.177
OH, T-THAT'S
NOT WHAT I ASKED.

24:13.177 --> 24:15.314
WHAT I ASKED WAS,
IS ANYONE IN SURVEILLANCE

24:15.314 --> 24:18.321
BREAKING ANY RULES
OR PROTOCOLS?

24:18.321 --> 24:20.793
NO.

24:25.370 --> 24:27.374
WELL...

24:27.374 --> 24:30.114
AT LEAST WE HAVE
EACH OTHER.

24:30.114 --> 24:31.450
THANK GOODNESS
FOR THAT.

24:39.869 --> 24:43.209
DID I EVER TELL YOU WANT TO BE
A NURSE HERE WHEN I GROW UP?

24:43.209 --> 24:45.948
NO.

24:45.948 --> 24:48.354
THAT'S COOL, THOUGH.

24:55.136 --> 24:56.873
I CAN HEAR YOUR HEART.

24:56.873 --> 25:00.414
YEAH, WELL, I HOPE SO.

25:00.414 --> 25:01.483
BUH-BUM.

25:01.483 --> 25:03.354
BUH-BUM.

25:03.354 --> 25:07.129
OH.
IT'S GETTING FASTER NOW.

25:10.303 --> 25:11.438
ARE YOU OKAY?

25:11.438 --> 25:14.278
YEAH,
IT'S JUST A HEADACHE.

25:14.278 --> 25:17.919
I'M ACTUALLY NOT SUPPOSED TO BE
LEAVING MY BED.

25:17.919 --> 25:19.858
WELL,
I'M GLAD YOU'RE OKAY.

25:19.858 --> 25:22.262
I'M GLAD YOU'RE OKAY.

25:22.262 --> 25:24.935
I NEVER REALLY
THOUGHT ABOUT IT BEFORE,

25:24.935 --> 25:28.476
BUT...
LAST NIGHT MADE ME REALIZE

25:28.476 --> 25:33.922
HOW AT ANY DAY, ANY POINT,
WE COULD JUST DIE.

25:33.922 --> 25:36.461
WE DIDN'T.

25:36.461 --> 25:38.298
WE'RE ALIVE.

25:46.181 --> 25:48.053
Theresa:
I THINK THAT TEACHER MEGAN'S

25:48.053 --> 25:49.289
BEEN WHISPERING IN HIS EAR.

25:49.289 --> 25:50.926
I CAN JUST FEEL IT.

25:50.926 --> 25:53.899
Ethan: I CAN'T STOP THINKING
ABOUT WHAT HE JUST SAID,

25:53.899 --> 25:56.939
ABOUT HOW I HAD THE GUY
AND THAT I LET HIM GO.

25:56.939 --> 25:59.478
THAT'S WHAT HAPPENED
WITH THE EASTER BOMBINGS.

25:59.478 --> 26:01.916
Man: <i>THIS NOW</i>
<i>JUST IN TO THE NEWS ROOM.</i>

26:01.916 --> 26:03.586
<i>WE ARE GETTING LIVE...</i>

26:03.586 --> 26:06.059
TERRORIST ATTACKS IN D.C. AND
LOS ANGELES AT THE SAME TIME.

26:06.059 --> 26:07.662
<i>...AND LOS ANGELES,</i>
<i>CALIFORNIA.</i>

26:07.662 --> 26:08.966
<i>ON AN EASTER DAY WHEN</i>
<i>SO MANY FAMILIES SPEND...</i>

26:08.966 --> 26:11.071
I GOT TO GO IN.

26:11.071 --> 26:13.175
ETHAN, DO YOU KNOW
SOMETHING ABOUT THIS?

26:13.175 --> 26:15.947
NO.
PLEASE TELL ME
WHAT'S GOING ON.

26:15.947 --> 26:17.919
I COULD NEVER TELL YOU.

26:17.919 --> 26:21.493
I WAS PART OF
A JOINT TERRORISM TASK FORCE.

26:21.493 --> 26:25.235
AND WE GOT WORD
THAT NARWAZ WAS DOWN IN MEXICO.

26:25.235 --> 26:30.113
SO WE WENT DOWN,
WE GRABBED HIM, SECURED HIM,

26:30.113 --> 26:33.487
PUT HIM ON A PLANE
TO TRANSPORT HIM BACK TO D.C.

26:33.487 --> 26:37.963
THEN I GOT A CALL
FROM HEADQUARTERS.

26:39.934 --> 26:41.605
TOLD ME TO LET HIM GO.

26:44.177 --> 26:46.348
THE GUY'S DIRTY.

26:46.348 --> 26:48.319
I KNEW HE WAS DIRTY.

26:48.319 --> 26:51.059
"LET HIM GO."

26:51.059 --> 26:53.931
WELL,
THAT'S EXACTLY WHAT I DID.

26:53.931 --> 26:55.234
IT WAS AN ORDER.

26:55.234 --> 26:59.177
AND THEN
THREE WEEKS LATER,

26:59.177 --> 27:02.717
621 PEOPLE
ARE MURDERED...

27:02.717 --> 27:04.989
BY NARWAZ AL-SALAAM.

27:04.989 --> 27:07.728
AND I HAD THE GUY

27:07.728 --> 27:10.301
AND I LET HIM GO.

27:14.243 --> 27:16.381
AND IT WAS CLASSIFIED.

27:16.381 --> 27:19.956
[ SIGHS ]

27:19.956 --> 27:21.626
YOU KNOW HOW BAD
I WANTED TO TELL YOU?

27:24.198 --> 27:26.337
THAT'S WHY
YOU WENT TO KATE.

27:26.337 --> 27:29.343
IT WAS THE TOUGHEST PERIOD
OF MY LIFE.

27:29.343 --> 27:31.983
[ SNIFFLES ]

27:31.983 --> 27:34.387
SHE WAS THERE.

27:34.387 --> 27:37.394
SHE WAS MY PARTNER.

27:37.394 --> 27:39.733
THERE'S NO EXCUSE
FOR WHAT HAPPENED AFTER THAT.

27:39.733 --> 27:43.140
[ SIGHS ]

27:43.140 --> 27:46.147
I'VE BEEN SORRY ABOUT IT
EVER SINCE.

27:46.147 --> 27:48.553
I'M NOT BLINDLY FOLLOWING
ORDERS ANYMORE.

27:48.553 --> 27:50.022
ELI: Sheriff.

27:50.022 --> 27:52.260
I'M SORRY.

27:52.260 --> 27:55.534
[ SIGHS ]

27:55.534 --> 27:57.773
YEAH.

27:57.773 --> 28:00.245
We have an emergency call
from the truck depot.

28:00.245 --> 28:03.051
YEAH, I'LL CHECK IT OUT.
THANKS.

28:08.797 --> 28:10.534
THANK YOU
FOR TELLING ME.

28:14.743 --> 28:17.416
I LOVE YOU.

28:25.801 --> 28:27.137
[ CLANG ]

28:28.240 --> 28:29.777
OH, I'M SORRY.

28:29.777 --> 28:31.547
[ Chuckling ]
I DIDN'T MEAN TO STARTLE YOU.

28:31.547 --> 28:33.818
I CAME
TO CHECK UP ON BEN.

28:33.818 --> 28:35.690
HOW'S HE DOING?

28:35.690 --> 28:38.262
YOU DON'T HAVE ANY CHILDREN
OF YOUR OWN, DO YOU?

28:38.262 --> 28:40.066
BRAD AND I HAVE NOT BEEN
SO BLESSED.

28:40.066 --> 28:43.340
YOU DO REALIZE THAT BEN
IS OUR SON AND NOT YOURS.

28:43.340 --> 28:46.112
THERESA,
WE ARE ON THE SAME TEAM.

28:46.112 --> 28:47.182
ARE WE?

28:47.182 --> 28:48.618
BECAUSE
I'M STARTING TO FEEL

28:48.618 --> 28:51.325
LIKE EVERY SINGLE THOUGHT
THAT YOU PUT INTO BEN'S HEAD

28:51.325 --> 28:53.095
IS SOMEHOW MEANT
TO UNDERMINE US.

28:53.095 --> 28:54.497
LET'S JUST BE
HONEST HERE.

28:54.497 --> 28:57.304
YOU'VE GOT AN AGENDA
AND I WANT TO KNOW WHAT IT IS.

28:57.304 --> 29:00.110
YOU'RE STARTING TO SOUND
A LITTLE PARANOID, THERESA.

29:00.110 --> 29:04.386
I SIMPLY BELIEVE THAT
THE CHILDREN OF WAYWARD PINES

29:04.386 --> 29:06.124
ARE THE FUTURE
OF WAYWARD PINES.

29:06.124 --> 29:09.130
AND TO THAT END, I TRY TO BE
AS HELPFUL AS POSSIBLE.

29:09.130 --> 29:11.135
HELPFUL RIGHT NOW
WOULD BE

29:11.135 --> 29:14.241
FOR YOU TO STAY
VERY FAR AWAY FROM MY FAMILY.

29:31.413 --> 29:32.816
HEY, SHERIFF.

29:32.816 --> 29:35.155
SO, WHAT HAPPENED?

29:35.155 --> 29:37.827
UH, I GOT HERE
ABOUT AN HOUR AGO.

29:37.827 --> 29:40.166
SOMEONE
SMASHED ONE OF OUR CAMERAS,

29:40.166 --> 29:43.573
CUT THE LOCK,
STOLE ONE OF OUR TRUCKS.

29:52.593 --> 29:54.597
WHAT KIND OF TRUCK
WAS IT?

29:54.597 --> 29:57.504
IT'S A 30-FOOT
DUMP TRUCK.

30:00.577 --> 30:02.949
WHAT'S GOING ON,
SHERIFF?

30:02.949 --> 30:06.424
IS THERE GONNA BE
ANOTHER BOMB?

30:06.424 --> 30:10.533
MAYBE THE TRUCK
IS THE BOMB.

30:18.216 --> 30:20.387
David:
WHAT ABOUT THE NIGHTMARES?

30:20.387 --> 30:22.526
NOTHING.

30:22.526 --> 30:24.429
LAST FEW YEARS.

30:24.429 --> 30:27.436
ANY EXPLANATION
FOR THAT?

30:27.436 --> 30:29.642
ACCEPTANCE,
I SUPPOSE.

30:31.746 --> 30:33.884
MY LIFE BEFORE,
I WAS ALWAYS

30:33.884 --> 30:37.793
RUNNING,
SEARCHING, FIGHTING.

30:37.793 --> 30:39.797
BUT THE QUESTIONS
I HAD THEN

30:39.797 --> 30:42.871
ARE NO DIFFERENT
THAN THE QUESTIONS I HAVE NOW.

30:42.871 --> 30:45.476
WHY ARE WE HERE?

30:45.476 --> 30:48.884
WHY DO WE BREATHE
IN AND OUT?

30:48.884 --> 30:51.523
IS THERE A GOD?

30:51.523 --> 30:55.933
BUT IF I'M HONEST...

30:55.933 --> 30:57.804
IN MY OLD LIFE,

30:57.804 --> 31:02.413
THERE WAS ALSO
A GREAT DEGREE OF FEAR.

31:02.413 --> 31:04.518
THERE WAS
TERROR EVERYWHERE.

31:04.518 --> 31:07.525
IT'S WHAT MY JOB
AS AN AGENT WAS ALL ABOUT.

31:07.525 --> 31:08.928
AND I WON'T LIE.

31:08.928 --> 31:11.467
I FED
ON THAT ADRENALINE.

31:11.467 --> 31:14.474
BUT HERE,
I DON'T KNOW.

31:14.474 --> 31:16.344
IT'S AS IF I'VE BEEN...

31:16.344 --> 31:19.919
FORCED TO LIVE
ONE MOMENT AT A TIME.

31:19.919 --> 31:22.659
I'M STILL ASKING
ALL THE SAME QUESTIONS,

31:22.659 --> 31:27.268
BUT THE ANSWERS
ARE LESS URGENT NOW.

31:27.268 --> 31:30.409
MAYBE BECAUSE
I FEEL SAFER.

31:30.409 --> 31:32.414
[ CHUCKLES ]

31:32.414 --> 31:35.821
HAVE YOU AND HAROLD,
UH,

31:35.821 --> 31:38.760
THOUGHT ANY MORE
ABOUT CHILDREN?

31:38.760 --> 31:41.500
MM, WE HAVE BEEN TALKING
ABOUT IT, YES.

31:41.500 --> 31:44.808
YOU'D MAKE
A GREAT MOM, KATE.

31:44.808 --> 31:47.012
HMM.
[ CHUCKLES ]

31:47.012 --> 31:50.754
OH,
CAN I GET THAT REFILL?

31:50.754 --> 31:53.493
OH. UH, YEAH.

31:55.030 --> 31:57.635
THANK YOU,
DR. JENKINS.

31:57.635 --> 31:58.772
THANK YOU, KATE.

32:01.411 --> 32:03.081
HMM.

32:10.965 --> 32:13.103
DR. JENKINS.

32:15.976 --> 32:19.083
WHY DIDN'T YOU COME AND TALK
TO ME BEFORE ALL THIS?

32:19.083 --> 32:21.823
YOU KNOW
I COULDN'T DO THAT.

32:21.823 --> 32:24.962
BESIDES,
WHAT WOULD YOU HAVE SAID?

32:24.962 --> 32:26.834
"FORGET THE TRUTH"?

32:26.834 --> 32:29.706
YOUR FRIEND TED
HAS DIED.

32:29.706 --> 32:32.580
TWO OF OUR YOUNGEST SERIOUSLY
INJURED IN THE HOSPITAL.

32:32.580 --> 32:34.116
OTHERS ARE MISSING.

32:34.116 --> 32:36.121
THAT'S THE PRICE
OF YOUR TRUTH.

32:36.121 --> 32:38.125
YOU KNOW
IT'S NOT LIKE THAT.

32:38.125 --> 32:40.597
YOU DIDN'T MEAN
FOR ANYONE TO DIE.

32:40.597 --> 32:42.969
HOW MANY MORE NEED
TO BE SACRIFICED?

32:42.969 --> 32:45.374
I THOUGHT YOU WERE HAPPY.

32:45.374 --> 32:47.111
I THOUGHT
WE MADE PROGRESS.

32:47.111 --> 32:49.584
I KNOW YOU DID.

32:49.584 --> 32:51.555
HOW CAN YOU BE
SO CHEERFUL

32:51.555 --> 32:55.430
WITH NEIGHBORS YOU'RE PUTTING
INTO LETHAL DANGER?

32:55.430 --> 32:58.503
ONLY A FANATIC
COULD BE SO CALLOUS.

32:58.503 --> 33:02.379
ARE YOU SURE
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT ME?

33:03.916 --> 33:06.655
BECAUSE IT SOUNDS LIKE
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT YOURSELF,

33:06.655 --> 33:08.492
DAVID PILCHER.

33:12.534 --> 33:15.073
HOW LONG
HAVE YOU KNOWN?

33:15.073 --> 33:18.949
DOESN'T MATTER.

33:18.949 --> 33:23.625
JUST PLEASE...TELL ME
WHAT THIS PLACE IS.

33:23.625 --> 33:26.999
YOU WERE
ITS MODEL CITIZEN.

33:28.569 --> 33:31.977
I THOUGHT THAT IF I -- I COULD
MAKE KATE HEWSON CONFORM,

33:31.977 --> 33:34.850
THEN I COULD
MAKE ANYONE CONFORM.

33:34.850 --> 33:37.489
THERE'D BE NO MORE NEED
FOR RECKONINGS.

33:37.489 --> 33:40.897
WHATEVER
YOU'RE TRYING TO DO HERE,

33:40.897 --> 33:43.202
IT WILL NEVER WORK
IF YOU KEEP PEOPLE IN THE DARK.

33:43.202 --> 33:46.676
IT'S NOT A QUESTION
OF KEEPING PEOPLE IN THE DARK.

33:46.676 --> 33:50.952
IT'S A QUESTION OF
KEEPING PEOPLE ALIVE.

33:50.952 --> 33:53.826
FREEDOM OR SAFETY.

33:53.826 --> 33:55.028
NOT BOTH.

33:55.028 --> 33:57.701
AND WHO ANOINTED YOU
TO MAKE THAT CHOICE?

33:57.701 --> 33:58.970
I DID.

34:04.549 --> 34:05.818
OH.

34:14.638 --> 34:16.810
THERE YOU GO.

34:16.810 --> 34:18.814
THANK YOU.

34:18.814 --> 34:21.687
I'M GETTING YOU
A PIECE OF PIE.

34:21.687 --> 34:25.062
DON'T WANT
THAT BLOOD SUGAR DROPPING.

34:27.834 --> 34:30.841
[ BEEP ]

34:30.841 --> 34:32.945
SECURITY.

34:43.235 --> 34:44.270
HEY.

34:52.222 --> 34:56.096
REGGIE HUDSON'S BEEN
DELETING SURVEILLANCE FOOTAGE.

34:56.096 --> 34:58.301
BUT YOU KNOW
THAT ALREADY.

34:58.301 --> 34:59.905
WELL, HE -- HE DID SHOW

34:59.905 --> 35:01.275
SOME SYMPATHY
FOR THE RESIDENTS.

35:01.275 --> 35:03.312
DID HE HELP THE PEOPLE
WHO BOMBED THE PERIMETER?

35:03.312 --> 35:05.751
NO. NO, DAVID.
NOT AT ALL.

35:05.751 --> 35:07.155
HE HAD NO IDEA THEY WERE --
HE'S A TRAITOR.

35:08.892 --> 35:10.529
HE NEEDS
TO BE TAKEN CARE OF.

35:10.529 --> 35:12.934
TAKEN CARE OF?

35:12.934 --> 35:15.273
DAVID, HE --
HE'S NO TRAITOR.

35:15.273 --> 35:17.544
HE'S --
WHY DON'T YOU
DEFINE TRAITOR.

35:17.544 --> 35:18.947
IS IT SOMEONE WHO LIES

35:18.947 --> 35:21.019
TO THE PEOPLE
WHO TRUST THEM THE MOST?

35:21.019 --> 35:23.591
YOU NEED TO PUNISH SOMEONE?
IS THAT IT?

35:23.591 --> 35:26.898
THEN PUNISH ME.
I'M THE ONE WHO LIED TO YOU.

35:26.898 --> 35:30.139
NOT REGGIE.
REGGIE TOLD THE TRUTH.

35:30.139 --> 35:32.878
THESE ARE OUR PEOPLE,
DAVID.

35:32.878 --> 35:35.784
THEY CAME TO US BY CHOICE,
NOT LIKE THE PEOPLE DOWN IN TOWN

35:35.784 --> 35:37.354
WHO DON'T KNOW
HOW THEY GOT THERE

35:37.354 --> 35:39.326
AND PROBABLY
WILL NEVER BE HAPPY.

35:39.326 --> 35:41.196
WE TOLERATED
THOSE RECKONINGS.

35:41.196 --> 35:44.670
"OKAY, WE'LL KILL ONE
AND KEEP THE REST IN LINE."

35:44.670 --> 35:47.677
BUT IF WE START
KILLING OUR OWN PEOPLE

35:47.677 --> 35:53.824
IN THE NAME OF SAVING HUMANITY,
THEN WE'VE LOST EVERYTHING.

35:53.824 --> 35:56.196
YOU NEED TO PUNISH, DAVID,
PUNISH ME.

35:56.196 --> 35:57.198
KILL ME.

36:03.912 --> 36:06.653
THERE WILL BE
NO MORE KILLINGS.

36:06.653 --> 36:08.223
DAVID.

36:08.223 --> 36:13.768
David: WE HAVE ALL HAD
TO ACCUSTOM OURSELVES

36:13.768 --> 36:17.910
TO THE METING OUT OF PUNISHMENT
IN WAYWARD PINES.

36:17.910 --> 36:21.886
BUT NOW,
WE ARE FORCED TO ADDRESS

36:21.886 --> 36:23.824
THE INSUBORDINATION
OF ONE OF OUR OWN.

36:23.824 --> 36:27.832
I HAVE ASKED YOU HERE
TO BEAR WITNESS.

36:27.832 --> 36:29.904
WE ALL KNOW REGGIE HUDSON.

36:29.904 --> 36:32.042
WE ALL LOVE REGGIE.

36:32.042 --> 36:36.919
BUT HIS MISTAKES HAVE LED
TO SERIOUS INJURY AND DEATH,

36:36.919 --> 36:39.692
AND THAT
CAN NO LONGER BE TOLERATED.

36:52.086 --> 36:53.757
[ CRYING ]

37:10.961 --> 37:13.367
ALL RIGHT.
OKAY.

37:13.367 --> 37:15.371
GOT IT.

37:17.341 --> 37:20.983
[ BOTH GRUNTING ]

37:20.983 --> 37:22.987
YOU READY?

37:24.724 --> 37:28.366
IT WASN'T
SUPPOSED TO GO LIKE THIS.

37:28.366 --> 37:30.037
LOOK.
I'M SORRY ABOUT KATE.

37:30.037 --> 37:33.043
THERE'S NOTHING WE CAN DO
ABOUT THAT NOW.

37:33.043 --> 37:35.381
I SAY WE JUST KEEP DRIVING
TILL WE HIT SAN FRANCISCO.

37:35.381 --> 37:38.188
THIS TIME TOMORROW, MAN, WE'LL
BE DRINKING BEERS BY THE BAY.

37:38.188 --> 37:40.192
[ SIGHS ]

37:40.192 --> 37:41.996
I CAN'T.

37:41.996 --> 37:44.134
YOU GOT TO BE
KIDDING ME.

37:44.134 --> 37:45.938
I CAN'T
LEAVE WITHOUT HER.

37:47.140 --> 37:49.145
HEY.

37:49.145 --> 37:51.284
YOU CHANGE YOUR MIND,

37:51.284 --> 37:53.722
YOU KNOW WHERE I'M GONNA BE
UNTIL THE SUN GOES DOWN.

37:53.722 --> 37:55.493
GOOD LUCK.

37:55.493 --> 37:57.497
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

38:18.476 --> 38:20.548
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

38:24.289 --> 38:26.161
HAROLD!

38:33.009 --> 38:34.346
[ GUNSHOTS ]

38:34.346 --> 38:35.815
LAST WARNING, HAROLD.

38:35.815 --> 38:38.421
GET ON YOUR KNEES.
PUT YOUR HANDS UP.

38:39.824 --> 38:41.895
[ GROANS ]

38:41.895 --> 38:43.799
GET UP.

38:46.105 --> 38:48.009
YOU ALMOST KILLED
MY SON.

38:48.009 --> 38:49.913
I SWEAR TO YOU
IT WAS AN ACCIDENT.

38:49.913 --> 38:51.316
WE JUST
WANTED TO GET OUT.

38:51.316 --> 38:52.819
WHERE ARE THE OTHERS?

38:52.819 --> 38:54.556
AAH, NO, IT'S JUST ME.
I'M THE ONLY ONE YOU WANT.

38:54.556 --> 38:57.029
I PLANNED THE WHOLE THING.
THEN WHERE ARE THEY?

38:57.029 --> 38:59.134
ARE YOU LISTENING TO ME?
NO, YOU LISTEN TO ME.

38:59.134 --> 39:01.539
NOW, I'M ABOUT THIS CLOSE
TO LETTING THEM

39:01.539 --> 39:03.343
CUT YOUR WIFE'S THROAT
IN THE MIDDLE OF MAIN STREET.

39:03.343 --> 39:06.349
WHERE ARE THEY?!
[ GROANS ]

39:10.993 --> 39:12.863
YOU'RE TOO LATE.

39:12.863 --> 39:14.367
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

39:16.037 --> 39:20.046
David: THESE ARE DANGEROUS TIMES
FOR ALL OF US.

39:20.046 --> 39:22.826
EVERYTHING
WE'VE RISKED OUR LIVES FOR

39:22.826 --> 39:24.627
WILL BE DESTROYED.

39:24.627 --> 39:29.432
WE'RE ENTERING A TIME OF WAR
WHERE NEW RULES MUST BE APPLIED.

39:29.432 --> 39:31.868
SECURITY MUST BE TIGHTENED,

39:31.868 --> 39:34.671
PROTOCOLS REINFORCED.

39:34.671 --> 39:40.276
EVERYTHING WE'VE ACHIEVED
HAS BEEN DUE TO YOUR HARD WORK.

39:40.276 --> 39:43.546
BUT WE'RE BATTLING TERRORISTS.

39:43.546 --> 39:45.548
SO STAY ALERT.

39:45.548 --> 39:47.117
STAY VIGILANT.

39:47.117 --> 39:49.753
REPORT ANYTHING SUSPICIOUS.

40:20.884 --> 40:23.620
[ GRUNTING, GROANING ]

40:35.865 --> 40:37.734
I GOT YOU.

40:37.734 --> 40:40.437
[ GRUNTS ]

40:49.179 --> 40:51.714
[ LAUGHS ]

40:51.714 --> 40:55.452
WE MADE IT, BUDDY.

40:55.452 --> 40:56.853
AH!

40:56.853 --> 40:59.556
[ LAUGHS ] WE MADE IT!

40:59.556 --> 41:02.425
[ LAUGHS ]

41:06.463 --> 41:07.597
[ GROWLS ]

41:07.597 --> 41:11.568
[ SCREAMING ]

41:16.739 --> 41:18.441
[ SCREECHES ]
